printstory: Astro and Playmate stumbled upon an old, tattered map while playing on the beach
Astro and Playmate took the map and decided to look for treasure
Astro and Playmate followed the clues on the map, walking through thick forests, crossing rivers, and climbing steep hills
Astro and Playmate encountered friendly animals who joined them on their quest
Astro and Playmate put down the map before entering the dark cave
Astro and Playmate reached the final clue and found themselves standing in front of a large, mysterious cave
Astro and Playmate entered the dark cave
Astro and Playmate  discovered a hidden chamber filled with glittering gold coins, sparkling jewels, and ancient artifacts
